<P>> I was curios if anyone has completed this quest. i got the hay,

<BR>&gt; took it to the high priest and he said that he cursed it and
<BR>&gt; said take this blood and straw and do evil with it, but he gave
<BR>&gt; me nothing, WTF, i had to pay him 7pp to do it and wasted a ton
<BR>&gt; of time going there. I'd like to know of broken quests before
<BR>&gt; devoting my time to it.please respond if you know anything about
<BR>&gt; this.
<P>go to Rivervale there is a vegetable guarden with a scarecrow, u give the magical sac of hay to a man standing near the scarecrow hail him first to make sure he is the right one .
<BR>Also u get the hay in west commons before quenos hills in a field u dont have to kill a scarecrow for one just look in the field for a bag(full of hay).
<P>
